To run this program:
First make sure, your scene image and myObjectTemplate.txt files are inside build folders.

Inside the build folder,change the model image name in: myObjectTemplate.txt  [ Ex. model.pcd ]

To execute the program do: ./template_alignment myObjectTemplate.txt scene.pcd

The result will be published in a output.pcd

To view the output do: pcl_viewer output.pcd scene.pcd
